+ The Solar_Auth_Adapter_Ini Class

++ Inheritance

* [Solar_Base::HomePage Solar_Base]

 * [Solar_Auth_Adapter::HomePage Solar_Auth_Adapter]

  * Solar_Auth_Adapter_Ini

++ Overview

Authenticate against .

ni style files.

Each group is a user handle, with keys for 'passwd', 'name', 'email',
and 'uri'.  For example:

<code>
[pmjones]
passwd = plaintextpass
email = pmjones@solarphp.com
name = Paul M. Jones
uri = http://paul-m-jones.com/
</code>